column3:
There is another simple QT5 change that you could include in this pull.

Line 5 of macdockiconhandler.mm can be changed from

```
#include <QtGui/QWidget>
```

to 

```
#include <QWidget>
```
Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/81605d90f53e5ab500f56927f4337bbc7f2d24f8 for binaries and test log.\n
